{"tid":1615624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［防具撚入］高級防彈材料免費任拎","createTime":"2019-10-03T07:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T14:07:11.000Z","uid":106799,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4396d92a1c59b0ee13c2125f64ae1efeef7f9791","tid":1615624,"uid":106799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"Sorry雖然係標題撚 但係講緊既就係周街都見到既banner<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ODfcZ7M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FODfcZ7M.png&h=1a9d518b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特別係保皇黨果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我禮拜日就係屋企做冷氣軍師 見到沙田人戰意高昂仲嘗試推近警方防線 不過就無一個合適既推進工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果當時有三面都圍晒banner既三角鐵馬 尖向警方防線 杋布做既banner可以擋晒最危險既布袋彈、橡膠子彈（卸走道力，因為呢啲子彈穿透力差，同樣原理都可以應用落雨傘）<br />\n<br />\n最重要係周街都有夠就手，唔洗錢，本身打晒窿用索帶就可以固定響任何野到，又係幫手清潔街上既垃圾（eg 保皇黨banner)<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"9c9d8fb34ddcf28cae54ce64123d5130fe9adecf","tid":1615624,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:09:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7c52656a69a179dc7b729fb1d286d6d92344783e","tid":1615624,"uid":106799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:09:52.000Z","msg":"覺得有用既 幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59482410d5d3d3ad760b75756fb073c46b1b9c17","tid":1615624,"uid":161404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2653c9721362ebbd440de7d499861d11b8d5cf9d","tid":1615624,"uid":106799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:13:29.000Z","msg":"自推之一"},{"pid":"383af89565ffad036a9d76f2fc35c621118d325a","tid":1615624,"uid":106799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"自推之二"},{"pid":"31853c5f0546625d405c0fc0c7114a4f6611bd34","tid":1615624,"uid":106799,"like"